The Renaissance Theatre Company production of Romeo and Juliet directed by Kenneth Branagh. A first-rate production with a first-rate cast (Branagh as Romeo and Samantha Bond as Juliet, plus Judi Dench, John Gielgud, Derek Jacobi etc) Kindly seed.
